overview: It's July 11th again, Tao Zhe is not only unhappy about the day he was born, but feels full of pressure and madness, because the master tape of the new album that should be handed over has not been made, and the progress is still a lot behind. cut. . . The record manager chased after Tao Zhe and washed his face with tears every day, while the boss chased his soul in three steps and fifty calls, and more...
title: Delivery Room 11
